TY  - JOUR
T1  - When a Queue Looks the Same to an Arriving Customer as to an Observer
AU  - Strauch, Ralph E.
Y1  - 1970/11/01
PY  - 1970
DA  - 1970/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.17.3.140
