N2  - In the paper ?Optimal Maintenance Policy and Sale Date of a Machine,? Dr. G. L. Thompson [Thompson, G. L. 1968. Optimal maintenance policies and sale date of a machine. Management Sci. 14(9, May) 543?550.] provided a model to interrelate economic life and maintenance policy, using Pontryagin's maximum principle. His results are very interesting, but these can be made more representative of the real life by a simple modification of the deterioration function d(t).
